document_data.name: Clan Kanjentellequor
document_data.mainbody: '''Clan Kanjentellequor''' was one of the [[dragonborn]] [[Thymari#Clans|clans]] of the nation of [[Tymanther]].
document_data.Description: Members of Clan Kanjentellequor used silver skewers through their jawline as their distinctive clan piercings.
document_data.History: As of [[1487 DR]], Clan Kanjentellequor has a sizable number of [[wizard]]s among its members.
document_data.Known members: * [[Kanjentellequor Biri]], a hero of the clan in [[1479 DR]].
